CRAFTING PATTERN - PREMIUM PDF DOWNLOAD
======================================
Pattern: Giraffe Amigurumi Plushie
Difficulty: Intermediate
Finished Size: 25cm tall

ABBREVIATIONS
ch = chain
sc = single crochet
inc = increase (2 sc in one stitch)
dec = decrease (sc 2 together)
sl st = slip stitch
st = stitch

INSTRUCTIONS
============
HEAD (Yellow Yarn)
Row 1: 6 sc in magic ring (6)
Row 2: inc in each st around (12)
Row 3: (sc, inc) around (18)
Row 4: (2 sc, inc) around (24)
Row 5: (3 sc, inc) around (30)
Row 6-12: sc in each st around (30)
* Place safety eyes between rows 9 and 10, 6 sts apart.
Row 13: (3 sc, dec) around (24)
Row 14: (2 sc, dec) around (18)
Row 15: (sc, dec) around (12)
* Stuff head firmly with fiberfill.
Row 16: dec around (6)
Fasten off and leave a long tail for sewing.

